Phase 7 – Intelligent Notification & Collaboration Agent

Implement a collaboration and notification layer on top of the existing RCA, RAG, Triage, and GitLab agents.

Objectives:

1. Microsoft Teams integration.
2. Email notification integration.
3. Dynamic team routing based on RCA category.
4. P1 executive summary generation.
5. Daily operational digest generation.
6. Weekly reliability insights report.
7. Notification history tracking.
8. Notification retry and failure handling.
9. Notification preferences management.
10. Incident timeline view combining RCA, GitLab, and notifications.

Create tables:

notifications

notification_recipients

notification_templates

Create APIs:

POST /api/notifications/send

GET /api/notifications

GET /api/notifications/{id}

POST /api/notifications/test

Design architecture for future LangGraph multi-agent orchestration and human approval workflows.
